OL,3,C'Missed opportunities' before bullied
OL,4,Cteen's suicide - coroner
OL,6,FA coroner has said there were "missed
OL,7,Fopportunities" to help a bullied
OL,8,Fteenager before she took her own life.
OL,10,FWillow-Tarriss Shannon Lynette Lee,
OL,11,Fknown as Ollie, was found dead at her
OL,12,Fhome in Barnsley on 6 October 2024
OL,13,Fafter a long struggle with her mental
OL,14,Fhealth.
OL,16,FAn inquest in Sheffield heard the 14-
OL,17,Fyear-old had "complex needs with
OL,18,Fsuspected neurodiversity" and
OL,19,F"identity confusion" and had been
OL,20,Fbullied at school.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
