OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778351322
OL,3,C'Missed opportunities' before bullied
OL,4,Cteen's suicide - coroner
OL,6,FHer mother Courtney Lee said the
OL,7,Fbullying had been "relentless".
OL,9,FRecording a conclusion of suicide,
OL,10,FAssistant Coroner Hannah Berry said
OL,11,Fthe teenager was on a waiting list for
OL,12,F"psycho social intervention", which
OL,13,Fshe was eligible to start four months
OL,14,Fbefore her suicide.
OL,16,FMs Berry added: "Due to poor
OL,17,Fcommunication between agencies Ollie
OL,18,Fwas discharged from the service due to
OL,19,Fno contact and therefore no psycho
OL,20,Fsocial intervention occurred.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778351322
OL,3,C'Missed opportunities' before bullied
OL,4,Cteen's suicide - coroner
OL,6,F"This was a missed opportunity for
OL,7,FOllie to remain under the care of
OL,8,Fmental health services."
OL,10,FThe hearing at Sheffield Medico-Legal
OL,11,FCentre was told Ollie had suffered
OL,12,Fhomophobic abuse, been dragged over
OL,13,Fgrass, sprayed with deodorant and told
OL,14,Fto harm herself by other pupils at
OL,15,FBarnsley Academy.
OL,17,FThe school failed to carry out risk
OL,18,Fassessments after she twice self-
OL,19,Fharmed in class.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778351322
OL,3,C'Missed opportunities' before bullied
OL,4,Cteen's suicide - coroner
OL,6,FMs Berry said: "There were additional
OL,7,Fmissed opportunities due to lack of
OL,8,Fcommunication when additional self
OL,9,Fharm attempts were not reported to
OL,10,Fmental health services."
OL,12,FThe assistant coroner said it could
OL,13,Fnot be said whether the failures
OL,14,F"caused or contributed to her death".
OL,16,FThe school had told the inquest it
OL,17,Fshould have drawn up safety support
OL,18,Fplans, but said it believed the
OL,19,Fsupport provided was "appropriate".
OL,26,@{D@bO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
