OL,3,C'Missed opportunities' before bullied
OL,4,Cteen's suicide - coroner
OL,6,FIn a statement after the inquest,
OL,7,FCourtney Lee, who is campaigning for
OL,8,Fbullying to be made a criminal
OL,9,Foffence, described her daughter as a
OL,10,F"unique, intelligent, funny and a
OL,11,Fbeautiful young girl whose emotions
OL,12,Fwere very complex".
OL,14,FShe added: "Despite everything
OL,15,Fcontained within records, reports,
OL,16,Fassessments and statements given at
OL,17,Fthe inquest the last three days, I ask
OL,18,Fthat Ollie is remembered first and
OL,19,Fforemost as a human being.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778351322
OL,3,C'Missed opportunities' before bullied
OL,4,Cteen's suicide - coroner
OL,6,F"She was not just a human being, she
OL,7,Fwas not just a mental health patient
OL,8,For a safeguarding concern or even a
OL,9,Fcollection of agency notes.
OL,11,F"She was my daughter, a friend, a
OL,12,Fperson with dreams, humour,
OL,13,Fintelligence, sensitivity and had an
OL,14,Fenormous amount emotional depth. She
OL,15,Fwas incredible.
OL,17,F"She mattered then and she matters
OL,18,Falways."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
