OL,3,C'Missed opportunities' before bullied
OL,4,Cteen's suicide - coroner
OL,6,FCarly Speechley, director of
OL,7,Fchildren's services at Barnsley
OL,8,FCouncil, said: "We are deeply saddened
OL,9,Fby the tragic death of a young student
OL,10,Fin Barnsley, and we extend our
OL,11,Fheartfelt condolences to their family,
OL,12,Ffriends, and all those affected.
OL,14,F"We can't comment on the details of
OL,15,Fthe inquest, however we take these
OL,16,Fmatters extremely seriously and will
OL,17,Fcarefully consider the findings set
OL,18,Fout in the coroner's report.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
